   <Ritual>
      <Nerangs id="ritualNerangs">
         <ab>Y59.29 Var. a (mss. 400, 2101, 88):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            <em>imat̰ barəsma</em>. ēn gyāg barsom az māhrōy stānišn datuš bē nibāyišn ud abāg gyāg ī xwēš bandišn frāgām pad bun ī barsom abāz kunišn abāg māhrōy nihišn</ab> 
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "At <em>imat̰ barəsma</em>, he has to remove the <em>barsom</em> from the <em>māhrōy</em>, to lay down the <em>datuš</em> and to bind it at its own place. 
            He has to remove the <em>frāgām</em> from the bottom of the <em>barsom</em> and put it on the <em>māhrōy</em>."</ab>  
         <ab>Y59.29 Var. b (mss. 5, 6, 15, 40, 82, 2106):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            <em>imat̰ barəsma</em>. ēn gyāg barsom az māhrōy gušādan ud datuš abāz gyāg ī xwēš kardan frāgām pad abāg bun ī barsom abāz kunišn abāg māhrōy nihišn</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "At <em>imat̰ barəsma</em>, he has to loose the <em>barsom</em> from the <em>māhrōy</em>, to bring the <em>datuš</em> back to its place. He has to remove the 
            <em>frāgām</em> from the bottom of the <em>barsom</em> and put it on the <em>māhrōy</em>."</ab>
      </Nerangs>
   </Ritual>
